        "content": "## MFA Lead Generation + Outbound Email Workflow\n\n**Trigger:** Manual (for now)\n**Future:** Change to Schedule trigger, run Mon/Wed/Fri at 8AM PST\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Pull leads from Apollo\n2. Enrich via Google Maps\n3. Enrich via SerpAPI (owner verification)\n4. Dedup + Scrub\n5. Generate personalized email with Claude\n6. Write to Google Sheets (Qualified / Discarded)\n7. Create Gmail Draft\n8. Output Summary",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 420
      },
